[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 301     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 302     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m The optimization needs to know how far every demand zone is from every potential facility location. Drive time is the standard metric in healthcare (not straight-line distance, which is meaningless in cities with rivers, highways, and traffic).
